WEBVTT

00:00:04.077 --> 00:00:05.067
So...

00:00:06.236 --> 00:00:07.600
What do you want to talk about?

00:00:08.270 --> 00:00:10.570
I've never asked this before in my life...

00:00:11.220 --> 00:00:13.013
I'm so nervous...

00:00:13.293 --> 00:00:14.903
It's okay! Take your time!

00:00:16.609 --> 00:00:18.152
Will you please...

00:00:20.305 --> 00:00:21.814
do push-ups for me?

00:00:22.488 --> 00:00:23.262
Of course!

00:00:24.380 --> 00:00:26.126
Eh? Push-ups?

00:00:26.511 --> 00:00:29.488
Can you do it now? Do push-ups.

00:00:29.802 --> 00:00:31.043
Push-ups?

00:00:32.894 --> 00:00:33.764
Sure.

00:00:45.141 --> 00:00:46.311
Sweat...

00:00:46.771 --> 00:00:48.451
Detected!

00:00:48.744 --> 00:00:51.214
Wherever there's someone sweating, 
we'll rush over!

00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.720
Carrying Ice Box on my back!

00:00:53.994 --> 00:00:55.544
And we'll swiftly set up...

00:00:55.544 --> 00:00:56.904
Break Time!

00:00:57.148 --> 00:00:57.908
We are...

00:00:57.908 --> 00:00:59.476
Ice de Breakers!

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:04.732
You're so cool! I'm a fan of yours!

00:01:05.857 --> 00:01:07.587
So cool...

NOTE Paragraph

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:09.750
I'm not sure what's going on here...

00:01:09.752 --> 00:01:11.652
But let's take a little break!

00:01:12.216 --> 00:01:13.456
Yes, please!

00:01:17.208 --> 00:01:18.869
Cheers!

00:01:19.135 --> 00:01:20.025
Cheers...

00:01:20.135 --> 00:01:23.215
Whenever, wherever,
Ice de Break!

00:01:23.828 --> 00:01:26.018
For those working hard,
they'll help out with Ice!

00:01:26.305 --> 00:01:30.305
The Ice de Breakers 
will still continue their work!

00:01:33.141 --> 00:01:34.387
Delicious!

00:01:35.729 --> 00:01:36.559
Yum!